 Nice day, nice 350th release!

 This game contains:
 ~ ART OF FIGHTING ~ BASEBALL STARS 2 ~ BURNING FIGHT ~ FATAL FURY ~
 ~ KING OF THE FIGHTERS 4 ~ KING OF THE MONSTERS ~ LAST RESORT ~ MAGICIAN LORD ~
 ~ METAL SLUG ~ NEO TURF MASTERS ~ SAMURAI SHODOWN ~ SENGOKU ~ SHOCK TROOPERS ~
 ~ SUPER SIDEKICKS 3 ~ TOP HUNTER ~ WORLD HEROES ~

 Enjoy!

